title: Population of the Netherlands 2019 , by age
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of inhabitants, containing a total of 5 data points.
In general Number of inhabitants has fallen over the Year.
Number of inhabitants is roughly constant from 0_-_20_years to 20_-_40_years, and lastly slightly decreasing from 20_-_40_years to 80_years_and_older.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 40_-_65_years and 65_-_80_years.
The highest Number of inhabitants, of value 5866334.0 was reached at Year 40_-_65_years
The lowest Number of inhabitants, of value 798820.0 was reported at Year 80_years_and_older
